title: 4 CDs of Pixies rarities, radio sessions, demos and more
description:
During the six years that they were together, the Pixies recorded four full albums and an EP, and a hell of a lot of other stuff, quite possibly all of it is here


I downloaded this amazing collection from here: <a href="
http://www.defgav.com/#pixies" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.defgav.com/#pixies</a>


Much credit to that guy for taking the time to assemble this collection


Also included in each folder is an image file with information on each track on each of the discs


Anyway, here&#039;s the tracklisting


Enjoy
